# svtest01-svelte-counter

A customizable text editor component built with Svelte 5, optimized for React/Next.js.

## Installation

```bash
npm install svtest01-svelte-counter
```

## Usage in React/Next.js

```tsx
'use client';
import { Editor, useEditor } from 'svtest01-svelte-counter';

export default function EditorPage() {
  const { text, setText } = useEditor('Initial text');

  return (
    <Editor
      text={text}
      size="medium"
      limit={100}
      onTextChange={setText}
    />
  );
}
```

## Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| text | string | '' | The editor content |
| size | 'small' \| 'medium' \| 'large' | 'medium' | The size of the editor |
| limit | number | 100 | Character limit |
| onTextChange | (text: string) => void | undefined | Callback for text changes |

## Custom Hook

The package includes a `useEditor` hook for easier state management:

```tsx
const { text, setText } = useEditor('Initial text');
```

